name: Kitty Golf
description:
It's my first time making a game that fast, and also without following a complete tutorial (why isn't there any 2d golf tutorial for Godot out there). So it may not be as great as it could but I'm really proud of this one.

No mobile version this time, had to cut some things to make it on time

I hit my head against a wall while playing basketball this Sunday (yes, a concussion, again...), so I couldn't work on my game for that day. I had to submit a really compact version of the game, it's a shame because I wasn't late on my schedule for once and I had loads of idead for good levels.
